{"calories":"630","carbs":69,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"\u003cp\u003eSometimes, bread and cheese is the perfect dinner—especially if it involves fluffy ricotta on sourdough topped with thyme-roasted tomatoes and truffle honey. For even more heartiness and flavor, we’ve added a salad of Parmesan, arugula, and crispy white beans to the mix, which gets tossed in Champagne vinaigrette. This is one classy, craveable meal.\u003c/p\u003e","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"d8320793fc","fat":33,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42745/yeYeMQfbSUee3LLnkgbw_Ricotta_Toasts_with_Truffle_Honey_and_White_Bean_Arugula_Salad___0113___HERO.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42745/hero_yeYeMQfbSUee3LLnkgbw_Ricotta_Toasts_with_Truffle_Honey_and_White_Bean_Arugula_Salad___0113___HERO.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42745/menu_small_yeYeMQfbSUee3LLnkgbw_Ricotta_Toasts_with_Truffle_Honey_and_White_Bean_Arugula_Salad___0113___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42745/small_square_yeYeMQfbSUee3LLnkgbw_Ricotta_Toasts_with_Truffle_Honey_and_White_Bean_Arugula_Salad___0113___HERO.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42745/medium_square_yeYeMQfbSUee3LLnkgbw_Ricotta_Toasts_with_Truffle_Honey_and_White_Bean_Arugula_Salad___0113___HERO.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42745/recipe_profile_page_yeYeMQfbSUee3LLnkgbw_Ricotta_Toasts_with_Truffle_Honey_and_White_Bean_Arugula_Salad___0113___HERO.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42747/pwpR3apTdaJ4Ehuv6K6P_Ricotta_Toasts_with_Truffle_Honey_and_White_Bean_Arugula_Salad___0103___THUMB.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42747/menu_small_pwpR3apTdaJ4Ehuv6K6P_Ricotta_Toasts_with_Truffle_Honey_and_White_Bean_Arugula_Salad___0103___THUMB.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42746/ryKCq9b1QtI4c3fu7hfI_Ricotta_Toasts_with_Truffle_Honey_and_White_Bean_Arugula_Salad___0112___MOBILE.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42748/large_cropped_I2gL5di8Sqethh9VeB6T_Ricotta_Toasts_with_Truffle_Honey_and_White_Bean_Arugula_Salad___0113___MAIN.jpg","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}}],"name":"Ricotta Toasts with Truffle Honey and White Bean–Arugula Salad","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"25-35","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":20,"public_slug":"white-bean-and-arugula-salad-with-truffle-honey-ricotta-toast","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/25859/recipe_card20180309-9-150w6vt.pdf","recipe_id":4315,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Ricotta Toasts","subtitle":"with Truffle Honey and White Bean–Arugula Salad","title":"Ricotta Toasts","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you'll be glad you did!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eUse the remaining truffle zest to sprinkle over popcorn or stir into a creamy pasta.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf your tomatoes have burst or broken down during roasting, don't worry! The toasts will still be delicious. Use a spoon to dollop the tomatoes over the ricotta. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eWait to toss the salad until just before you serve so the arugula stays vibrant and the roasted beans keep their crisp texture.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["2 baking sheets","8\" small pan"],"id":4315,"ingredients":["15-ounce can white beans","grape tomatoes","baby arugula","shallot","thyme","Champagne vinegar","Dijon mustard","sourdough bread","ricotta cheese","honey","truffle zest","shaved Parmesan cheese"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"15-ounce can white beans","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/551/medium_square_canellini-beans.jpg"},{"name":"grape tomatoes","quantity":"0.5","measurementUnit":"pint","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/191/medium_square_GRAPE_TOMATOES_copy.jpg"},{"name":"baby arugula","quantity":"3.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/239/medium_square_arugula-test.jpg"},{"name":"shallot","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/130/medium_square_SHALLOT_copy.jpg"},{"name":"thyme","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1289/medium_square_medium_square_herb-thyme-fresh.jpg"},{"name":"Champagne vinegar","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/252/medium_square_vinegar-champagne-2.jpg"},{"name":"Dijon mustard","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/37/medium_square_dijon-test.jpg"},{"name":"sourdough bread","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"slice","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/45/medium_square_SOUR_DOUGH.jpg"},{"name":"ricotta cheese","quantity":"4.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1486/medium_square_RICOTTA_CHEESE_-4386_copy.jpg"},{"name":"honey","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/142/medium_square_HONEY_copy.jpg"},{"name":"truffle zest","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1661/medium_square_truffle_zest.jpg"},{"name":"shaved Parmesan cheese","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/2327/medium_square_dairy-cheese-shredded2.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"olive oil","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":14,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":15,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare ingredients","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42749/recipe_card_size_QBpDyc6HTmaUBAWFsOJv_1._Prepare_Ingredients.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 450°F. Drain and rinse\u003cstrong\u003e white beans\u003c/strong\u003e. Pat \u003cstrong\u003e1 cup beans\u003c/strong\u003e dry with paper towel, then place on a baking sheet (save remaining beans for another recipe—we love adding them to chili). Rinse \u003cstrong\u003etomatoes\u003c/strong\u003e. Rinse \u003cstrong\u003earugula\u003c/strong\u003e and pat dry with paper towel. Peel \u003cstrong\u003eshallot\u003c/strong\u003e, halve, and thinly slice. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Roast beans and tomatoes","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42750/recipe_card_size_wIjNFJkQDWqy3225Pm86_2._Roast_Beans_and_Tomatoes.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eToss \u003cstrong\u003ewhite beans\u003c/strong\u003e on baking sheet with \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired, then arrange on 1 half of baking sheet. On other half, toss \u003cstrong\u003ewhole thyme springs \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003etomatoes\u003c/strong\u003e with \u003cstrong\u003e.5 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. Roast until beans are slightly browned and crispy and tomatoes are tender, 12-15 minutes. Remove from oven and set aside. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Make dressing","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42751/recipe_card_size_HWsneqsJQP0qcbarmFvw_3._Make_Champagne_Vinaigrette.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile beans and tomatoes roast, heat \u003cstrong\u003e.5 tablespoon olive oil \u003c/strong\u003ein a small pan over medium heat. When oil is shimmering, add \u003cstrong\u003eshallot\u003c/strong\u003e and cook until softened, about 5 minutes. Transfer to a large bowl (big enough for the salad), and whisk in \u003cstrong\u003eChampagne vinegar\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.5 packet mustard \u003c/strong\u003e(discard remainder), \u003cstrong\u003e2 tablespoons olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. Set aside until Step 6.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Toast bread and make truffle honey","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42753/recipe_card_size_1ffYuoS1RjeyX1uAXYqT_4._Toast_Bread_and_Make_Truffle_Honey_2X.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eOn a separate baking sheet, arrange \u003cstrong\u003ebread slices\u003c/strong\u003e in a single layer and toast until golden, 4-5 minutes. Meanwhile, in a small bowl, stir together \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of ricotta \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003e1 teaspoon olive oil \u003c/strong\u003eto fully combine (save remaining ricotta for a snack). In a separate small bowl, stir together \u003cstrong\u003ehoney\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.5 packet truffle zest \u003c/strong\u003e(see recipe tip), and \u003cstrong\u003e.25 teaspoon salt \u003c/strong\u003eto fully combine. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Assemble ricotta toasts","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42752/recipe_card_size_pICx7fSQT9Oe7rNsLKEk_5._Assemble_Ricotta_Toasts.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eOnce toasted, remove \u003cstrong\u003ebread slices\u003c/strong\u003e from oven and halve crosswise, then spread over \u003cstrong\u003ericotta mixture\u003c/strong\u003e. Once beans and tomatoes are roasted, remove and discard \u003cstrong\u003ewhole thyme sprigs\u003c/strong\u003e. Top \u003cstrong\u003etoasts\u003c/strong\u003e with \u003cstrong\u003eroasted tomatoes\u003c/strong\u003e and drizzle over \u003cstrong\u003etruffle honey \u003c/strong\u003e(see recipe tip). \u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Finish arugula salad and plate","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/42754/recipe_card_size_t9zvpykUSVeIZKfE30Xo_6._Plate.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eAdd \u003cstrong\u003eParmesan\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003earugula\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003eroasted white beans \u003c/strong\u003eto bowl with dressing and toss to coat (see recipe tip). Divide \u003cstrong\u003ewhite bean-arugula salad\u003c/strong\u003e between serving plates and serve alongside \u003cstrong\u003ericotta toasts\u003c/strong\u003e. Dig in!\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"quick prep","slug":"quick-prep","hex_color":null}],"allergens":[{"name":"Soy","slug":"soy","hex_color":""},{"name":"Egg","slug":"egg","hex_color":""},{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""},{"name":"Tree Nuts","slug":"tree nuts","hex_color":""},{"name":"Wheat","slug":"wheat","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Bread","slug":"bread","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"quick prep","slug":"quick-prep","hex_color":null}],"feature":[]}}